Title: Lesleyann Reilly
DateModified: '2019-02-14'
DatePublished: '2019-02-14'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/lesleyann-reilly
SetInCountry: Ireland
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Lesleyann Reilly
AuthorCountry: Ireland
Text: An actress in search of a new life,  travels to a small town and meets an old
  antique dealer. She's stricken by a certain antique in his shop and he tells her
  a story about the origin of the antique. When she hears about the owner of the antique
  and the story behind it she is confronted with something so incredibly strange and
  terrifying , but intriguing. However been drawn to the world of the old antique
  may require a total abandonment of her current life.
